**Overall Meaning:**

This verse emphasizes the importance of recognizing the divine within all beings and the true nature of the Self. It instructs to worship the divine, who resides in all beings and is the lord of all, as the Self. By seeing this Self, which is the form of knowledge and free from all limitations, one realizes true liberation and perfection. 
